      </complexType>
   </element>

   <annotation>
      <appInfo>
         <meta.section type="examples"/>
      </appInfo>
      <documentation>
         Here is an example of regisering a new resource task provider:

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
   &lt;extension
         point=&quot;com.google.eclipse.mechanic.resourcetaskproviders&quot;&gt;
      &lt;scanner
            class=&quot;com.google.eclipse.mechanic.MyTaskProvider&quot;&gt;
      &lt;/scanner&gt;
   &lt;/extension&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
